name: QR Code Generator
description:
‘QR Code Generator’ helps you to quickly create a Vector QR code.
Just enter your content or URL then click ‘Place QR code’ — or CMD/Control + Enter.

This is also great for creating a QR code to share the Figma file link – or a link to your prorotype.

Tip: On iOS – the built in camera app can scan QR codes.
